msgctxt "an5.287-292:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.287-292:0.2"
msgid "28. Sikkhāpadapeyyāla "
msgstr "28. Abbreviated Texts on Training Rules "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.287-292:0.3"
msgid "287–292. Bhikkhunīsuttādi "
msgstr "287–292. A Nun "

# NOTE: I didlike “probationer” for sikkhamana, as it might suggest she has been placed on probation. As i understand it, this was a special status for girls in their late teens.
#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an5.287-292:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgatā bhikkhunī … pe … sikkhamānā … sāmaṇero … sāmaṇerī … upāsako … upāsikā yathābhataṃ nikkhittā evaṃ niraye. "
msgstr "“A nun … trainee nun … novice monk … novice nun … layman … laywoman … with five qualities is cast down to hell. "

msgctxt "an5.287-292:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "an5.287-292:1.3"
msgid "Pāṇātipātinī hoti, adinnādāyinī hoti, kāmesumicchācārinī hoti, musāvādinī hoti, surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhāyinī hoti. "
msgstr "They kill living creatures, steal, commit sexual misconduct, lie, and use alcoholic drinks that cause negligence. "

msgctxt "an5.287-292:1.4"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgatā upāsikā yathābhataṃ nikkhittā evaṃ niraye. "
msgstr "With these five qualities they’re cast down to hell. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an5.287-292:2.1"
msgid "Pañcahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgatā upāsikā yathābhataṃ nikkhittā evaṃ sagge. "
msgstr "A nun … female intern … novice monk … novice nun … layman … laywoman … with five qualities is raised up to heaven. "

msgctxt "an5.287-292:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "an5.287-292:2.3"
msgid "Pāṇātipātā paṭiviratā hoti, adinnādānā paṭiviratā hoti, kāmesumicchācārā paṭiviratā hoti, musāvādā paṭiviratā hoti, surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānā paṭiviratā hoti. "
msgstr "They don’t kill living creatures, steal, commit sexual misconduct, lie, or use alcoholic drinks that cause negligence. "

msgctxt "an5.287-292:2.4"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgatā upāsikā yathābhataṃ nikkhittā evaṃ sagge”ti. "
msgstr "With these five qualities they’re raised up to heaven.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.287-292:2.5"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

